---
title: Jarvis — OIDC login flow (Authorization Code + PKCE)
config:
  theme: neutral
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Browser
    participant J as Jarvis backend
    participant O as OIDC provider

    U->>J: GET /auth/oidc/start
    J->>J: generate code_verifier + code_challenge,<br/>set state cookie
    J-->>U: 302 redirect to issuer<br/>(with code_challenge)
    U->>O: authenticate (login form / SSO session)
    O-->>U: 302 redirect to<br/>/auth/oidc/callback?code=...&state=...
    U->>J: GET /auth/oidc/callback?code=...&state=...
    J->>J: verify state (CSRF check)
    J->>O: exchange code for tokens<br/>(sends code_verifier)
    O-->>J: ID token + access token
    J->>J: verify ID token,<br/>UpsertOIDCUser by sub,<br/>map admin role from configured claim
    J-->>U: Set-Cookie: jarvis_session (HttpOnly, SameSite=Lax)<br/>302 redirect to /
